0x53AB5C35.name: SET_VEHICLE_WHEEL_SIZE

params.name: vehicle
params.description: The vehicle to set data for.

params.name: size
params.description: Size of the wheels (usually between 0.5 and 1.5 is reasonable).

0x53AB5C35.description:
Sets vehicle's wheels' size (size is the same for all the wheels, cannot get/set specific wheel of vehicle).
Only works on non-default wheels.
Returns whether change was successful (can be false if trying to set size for non-default wheels).
0x53AB5C35.resultsDescription: Bool - whether change was successful or not
